0vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827330" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的吕茵（图片来源：BBC 和兰伯特工作室）</figcaption></figure><p>由于叛徒们受到她作为传播学博士的怀疑和智慧的威胁，尹律成为第三季中第一个被谋杀的参赛者。</p><p><strong>被放逐：内森·海德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827328" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827328" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827328" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg" alt="内森在《叛徒》中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827328" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的内森 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管圆桌会议上对叛徒琳达的怀疑越来越多，八名玩家还是投票罢免了 39 岁的房地产顾问内森。除了他安静的举止之外，这个决定所依据的证据很少。</p><p><strong>被谋杀者：基思·斯图尔特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827333" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827333" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827333" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的基思" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827333" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的基思 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>窗户清洁工基思被认为是该组织中坚强而可爱的角色，他成为第二个被叛徒谋杀的人。</p><p><strong>被放逐：艾伦·温（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827334" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827334" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827334" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的艾伦" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827334" class="wp-caption-text">埃伦在《叛徒》中被放逐（图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert）</figcaption></figure><p>在被其他玩家认为可疑，再加上她相信大多数叛徒都是“坚强的女性”后，翻译埃伦被逐出了游戏。</p><p> “一旦你的名字被曝光，你就很难自救，”她告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/crrw4d1lxygo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>。</p><p><strong>被放逐：Armani Gouveia（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的阿玛尼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827329" class="wp-caption-text">阿玛尼是第三季第一个离开的叛徒 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在第三集中，玩家们成功地驱逐了他们的第一个叛徒，因为阿玛尼的傲慢和指挥方式很快就对她产生了不利影响。在她自己的妹妹玛雅·古维亚 (Maia Gouveia) 承认对她的行为表示怀疑后，她的命运就注定了。</p><h2>第二周谁离开了？</h2><p>在第二周节目开始时，之前被淘汰的参赛者亚历山大·德拉戈内蒂、福齐亚·法西尔和杰克·马里纳-布朗被带回来参加挑战，他们被吊在森林的笼子里。</p><p>玩家只能拯救三名悬挂参赛者中的两名，然后他们将从此时开始加入游戏。在提出令人信服的论据后，亚历山大和福齐亚被玩家救了出来，而出生于约克郡的市场交易员<strong>杰克则被送回家</strong>。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：玛雅·古维亚（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827331" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827331" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827331" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的玛雅" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827331" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的玛雅 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在她的妹妹在最后一次圆桌会议上被放逐后，叛徒们选择谋杀玛雅，以消灭可能是强大的对手。她的死也让弗雷迪产生了怀疑，弗雷迪此前曾在上一次圆桌会议上针对她。</p><p><strong>被放逐：卡西姆·艾哈迈德（忠实者）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827327" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827327" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827327" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的卡西姆" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827327" class="wp-caption-text">卡西姆被放逐让所有人都感到沮丧 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>不幸的是，卡西姆不可避免地被逐出小组，因为他太友善了，而且——至少在杰克看来——因为他是一名医生。阿玛尼在上一次圆桌会议上莫名其妙地为他担保后，决定了他的命运，让其他玩家相信他也是叛徒。</p><p><strong>被放逐：泰勒·史密斯（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827710" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827710" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827710" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new.jpg" alt="叛徒泰勒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827710" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的泰勒 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管弗雷迪受到了激烈的批评，但圆桌会议上的局势却转向了对 29 岁理发师泰勒的不利，因为里昂和莉安开始怀疑他们核心圈子里的某个人。他的离开引起了利维特别情绪化的反应，她因为这个决定而泪流满面。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：利维·迪恩（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3828057" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828057" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828057" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors.jpg" alt="利维叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828057" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的利维 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>为了让弗雷迪进一步陷入困境，叛徒决定杀死 26 岁的美容师兼模特莉维，因为她在圆桌会议上情绪爆发。</p><p><strong>被放逐：丹·伯德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3828064" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828064" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828064" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的丹" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828064" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的丹 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管在这一集之前没有引起任何人的注意，但丹在挑战期间的谎言却成为了他在圆桌会议上的失败。 Leanne 和 Minah 与他对峙，他们向团队其他成员展示了他隐藏的真相。</p><h2>第三周谁离开了？</h2><p>第三周的第一起谋杀案出现了转折。叛徒们挑选了四名参赛者来玩一种名为“死亡竞赛”的纸牌游戏，失败者将被谋杀。</p><p>莱昂、亚历山大、福西亚和安娜被选中参加比赛。每轮的获胜者都免遭谋杀。</p><p>剩下的玩家在下一个任务中发现了游戏的结果，他们在棺材里找到了幸存的玩家。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：福齐亚·法西尔（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="福齐亚·法西尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829330" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的福齐亚 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在与莱昂进行了一场紧张的决赛后，福齐亚是死亡竞赛结束时最后一个还活着的选手。然后她在众目睽睽之下被叛徒杀害。</p><p><strong>被放逐：琳达·兰兹（叛徒​​）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829332" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829332" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829332" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors.jpg" alt="琳达" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829332" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的琳达 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>经过几天忠实信徒的怀疑，包括圆桌会议上的几次千钧一发，琳达成为第二个被逐出游戏的叛徒。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：安娜·杜克（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829726" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829726" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829726" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1.jpg" alt="安娜·杜克" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829726" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的安娜 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>夏洛特被招募为叛徒后，她和米娜决定安娜在城堡的时间已经结束，“不再需要”她。安娜在游戏早期就被怀疑是叛徒，在被选中参加死亡竞赛后，她感觉叛徒是来抓她的。叛徒之前曾试图招募她，但她拒绝了。</p><p><strong>被放逐：亚历克斯·奥莱克西（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829736" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829736" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829736" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的亚历克斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829736" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的亚历克斯。图片来源：BBC/兰伯特工作室</figcaption></figure><p>整场比赛中，亚历克斯基本上都在雷达下飞行，但厨房里的一次不恰当的评论证明了他的失败。</p><p><strong>被谋杀者：丽莎·库普兰（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831243" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831243" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831243" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors.jpg" alt="丽莎·库普兰《叛徒》" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831243" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的丽莎 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>叛徒们看到她作为一个值得信赖的信徒的力量，不能在理论上说谎，经过一番敏锐的观察后，叛徒们决定谋杀英国圣公会牧师丽莎。</p><p><strong>被放逐：莱昂·杰克曼（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831242" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831242" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831242" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors.jpg" alt="莱昂叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831242" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的莱昂 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>零售店经理莱昂在死亡竞赛后态度发生变化，忠实信徒开始怀疑他，导致他最亲密的盟友转而反对他。</p><h2>第四周谁离开了？</h2><p>该剧的最后一周以相对直接的方式开始，有一场残酷的谋杀和一场扭曲的国际象棋比赛。</p><p>圆桌会议只剩下两场，剩下的八名参赛者之间的紧张关系达到了历史最高点。然而，这个游戏即将通过一种被嘲笑的秘密力量而被彻底颠覆。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：乔·斯科特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831230" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831230" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831230" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors.jpg" alt="乔·斯科特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831230" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的乔。图片来源：BBC/StudioLambert</figcaption></figure><p>乔是该小组中一位非常直言不讳的成员，经常在圆桌会议上提出想法——无论这些想法最终被证明是错误的。然而，这最终对他不利，因为叛徒认为谋杀他会发出强烈的信息。</p><p><strong>被放逐：米娜·香农（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831236" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831236" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831236" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="米纳" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831236" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的米亚。图片来源：BBC/StudioLambert</figcaption></figure><p>米娜从一开始就扮演了叛徒的角色，并在相当长的一段时间内避免了怀疑，但最终，这一切都失败了。最后，叛徒夏洛特把她扔到了公共汽车下，进行了最后的投票，这意味着她被逐出了城堡。</p><p>被淘汰后，最后一个叛徒夏洛特选择招募弗雷迪，弗雷迪无奈地接受了邀请。</p><p><strong>被放逐：弗雷迪·弗雷泽（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831608" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831608" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831608" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors.jpg" alt="弗雷迪·弗雷泽" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831608" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的弗雷迪。图片来源：BBC/StudioLambert</figcaption></figure><p>在该剧的倒数第二集中，夏洛特欺骗了新招募的叛徒弗雷迪谋杀了莱恩，尽管事实上她有盾牌，所以无法被谋杀，但没有发生谋杀。忠实信徒识破了弗雷迪笨拙的撒谎企图，随后他被放逐了。</p><p>在任务中赚到最多的钱后，弗朗西斯卡被赋予了先知的力量，使她能够在一次私人会议中发现一名选定参赛者的真实身份。在戏剧性的悬念中，我们发现她选择揭开夏洛特的面具。</p><p><strong>被放逐：夏洛特·伯曼（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831925" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831925" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831925" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors.jpg" alt="夏洛特叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831925" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的夏洛特（BBC/Studio Lambert）</figcaption></figure><p>弗兰西斯卡发现夏洛特是叛徒后，两人为了让其他人相信昨晚的事情而展开了一场激烈的战斗。尽管夏洛特流下了鳄鱼的眼泪，但弗朗西斯卡还是成功地推翻了最后的叛徒——尽管夏洛特离开时，没有一个忠实信徒被告知她的真实身份。</p><p><strong>被放逐：亚历山大·德拉戈内蒂（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831929" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831929" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831929" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors.jpg" alt="叛徒中的亚历山大" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831929" class="wp-caption-text">亚历山大在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在最后的圆桌会议上绊倒后，亚历山大成为了火炉周围的明显目标。尽管他是一个忠实的人，但他在整个系列赛中都被怀疑，并且这些怀疑在最后一轮中变得太突出了。</p><p><strong>放逐：弗朗西斯卡·罗恩·普洛登（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831928" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831928" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831928" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main.jpg" alt="弗朗西斯卡叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831928" class="wp-caption-text">弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>夏洛特（Charlotte）对弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）的信誉的袭击事实证明，在壁炉比赛中造成了巨大破坏，因为她成为莱恩（Leanne）的关键投票后，在最后一轮比赛中被驱逐出境。</p><h2>谁赢得了<em>叛徒</em>的决赛？</h2><p><strong>获奖者：杰克·布朗（Jake Brown）和Leanne Quigley（信徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831930" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831930" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831930" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners.jpg" alt="杰克和莱恩叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831930" class="wp-caption-text">杰克（Jake）和莱恩（Leanne）在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>今年的系列赛由28岁的项目经理杰克（Jake）和28岁的莱恩（Leanne）赢得，他是指甲技术员的前士兵。在壁炉中取消了亚历山大和弗朗西斯卡之后，两人将94,600英镑的最终奖项分配。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-killed-3827323">谁赢得了“叛徒”第三季的职位？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
